8 activity is proposed as identified in tide tables published as determined by the United States
9 Department of Commerce, National Ocean Service Oceanic and Atmospheric
10 Administration. Coastal wetlands may include portions of coastal sand dunes.
11 SUMMARY
1122 This bill amends the definition of "coastal wetlands" in the Natural Resources
